title: September 2025 Development Sprint
content: This two-day period represents intense activity in the SkogAI realm. Multiple new scripts were created ($.sh, git.sh, foo.sh, type.sh), existing scripts were heavily modified, and execution counts spiked dramatically. The sprint culminated in type.sh reaching 66 executions, suggesting rapid prototyping and iterative development of new capabilities.
summary: A concentrated period of script development and testing from September 19-20, 2025
